title: OPL Top 5 plays

embed.description: The best plays and moments of OPL Split 1 Week 4 & 5. Feel free to support the scene by liking and sharing this video with a mate. Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/duoqueuelol Facebook: http://facebook.com/duoqueuelol Website:http://duoqueue.net.au Created by @Jason_OCE & @GrandJason

body:
I've been making highlight videos of the OPL Top 5 plays, and just realised I've never shared them with you guys here.

Everyone's favorite episode appears to be number 2 ( the editing at the number 1 play tho ) but here's our latest episode.

What do you guys think? :)

~J

replies.body: Nice, i like it man, keep up this awesome work
